he_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Arrival of the Andals.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_sunspear.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_sunspear.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne: Sunspear.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_21\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 21\">Chapter 21</a>, The Queenmaker.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_norvos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_norvos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Norvos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_wi